            "title": "即月期指開報21311點 低水155點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報21311點，跌176點，較上日現貨收市價21466點低水155點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報4929點，跌60點，低水53點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報7894點，跌76點，低水89點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14858160-%e5%8d%b3%e6%9c%88%e6%9c%9f%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%a0%b121311%e9%bb%9e-%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4155%e9%bb%9e",
